This is a Bitcoin miner engine written in flash actionscript3.
The code is used in http://www.bitppt.com/

Please notice
This code includes just making sha256 hash faster than Flash mx library
and judge it if it's a valid block for Bitcoin network to send.

*No getWork() function from Bitcoin server. 
*No sending work function to bitcoin network.
*Speed is arround 50Kh/s to 80Kh/s

